BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 738.00 Td (Sustainability robotics focuses on designing robotic systems that support environmental,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 723.83 Td (social, and resource-aware goals.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 685.15 Td (Examples include robots that monitor ecosystems, inspect water infrastructure, support) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 670.98 Td (precision agriculture, assist disaster response, reduce human exposure to hazardous) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 656.80 Td (environments, or help maintain renewable energy systems.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 618.13 Td (Sustainability also affects design choices. A sustainable robot should consider energy use,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 603.95 Td (maintenance, repairability, local context, data responsibility, and the long-term) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 589.78 Td (consequences of deployment.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 551.10 Td (Scene 7: Bio-Inspired Systems) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 503.70 Td (Bio-inspired robotics studies patterns from living systems and uses them to guide robotic) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 489.53 Td (design.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 450.85 Td (Birds inspire aerial robots. Insects inspire swarm behavior. Fish inspire underwater robots.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 436.68 Td (Human and animal motion inspire walking, grasping, and adaptive movement.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 398.00 Td (The point is not to copy nature exactly. The point is to learn from proven biological) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 383.83 Td (strategies and adapt them to engineering problems.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 345.15 Td (Scene 8: Applied Example) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 297.75 Td (Imagine a small autonomous robot designed to inspect a water channel after heavy rainfall.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 259.08 Td (It needs sensors to detect position, water level, and obstacles. It needs actuators to move) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 244.90 Td (through uneven terrain. It needs a controller to choose safe motion. It needs feedback to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 230.73 Td (stay on course. It also needs sustainable design decisions: low energy use, safe materials,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 216.55 Td (easy maintenance, and a clear benefit to the community.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 177.88 Td (This example shows how the technical and sustainability sides of robotics must work) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 163.70 Td (together.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 125.03 Td (Scene 9: Checkpoint) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 77.63 Td (Pause and answer this question:) Tj ET
